(***Fresh water tank system control and monitoring***)
(*Requirements:
- Needs to regulate fresh water storage tank level
- Needs to refill fresh water storage tank level with a FWStorageTankFillingValve
- All tanks need to be able to drain water into collecting tank/outside of the ship
- Service tank needs to regulate the tank level to a specific level to optimize steam production, this is to be configurable
- Service tank needs to be drained into collecting tank/outside of the ship
- FWFeed pumps will work with the duty change over, change over occurs on demand by the operator or by a fault in the device
- Changeover is only if pumps are in automatic mode, other mode is manual
- FWFeed pumps pump water from the storage tank to the service tank*)

